==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unassured
<hw>Un`as*sured"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
assured; not bold or confident.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not to be trusted.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not insured against loss; <as>as, <ex>unassured</ex>
goods</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unatonable</ent>⟦br⟧
